ing%20essential%20in%20workplaces%2C%20with%20leaders%20urging%20its%20adoption.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20venture%20capitalist%20is%20playing%20the%20AI%20game%20by%20investing%20in%20tools%20for%20top%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BUncapped%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-40-best-women-early-stage-vc-investors-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKleiner%20Perkins%3C%2Fa%3E%20partner%2C%20Mamoon%20Hamid%2C%20said%20the%20firm%20is%20investing%20in%20startups%20that%20make%20digital%20assistants%20for%20America's%20highest-paying%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you'd%20look%20at%20a%20chart%20of%20the%20top%2020%20jobs%20in%20the%20US%20by%20pay%2C%20those%20are%20doctors%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20engineers%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamid%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20thought%2C%20OK%2C%20so%20how%20do%20we%20invest%20in%20copilots%20for%20these%20job%20types%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VC%20added%20that%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20parts%20of%20these%20jobs%20that%20are%20very%20nuanced%20and%20the%20human%20brain%20needs%20to%20process%20those%20parts%20of%20the%20job%2C%20but%20there's%20parts%20that%20AI%20is%20scribing%20or%20taking%20notes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamid%20said%20that%20the%20company%20had%20invested%20in%20Ambience%2C%20a%20startup%20for%20doctors%2C%20Harvey%2C%20a%20legal-tech%20platform%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flexisnexis-harvey-form-strategic-alliance-amid-growing-competition-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0for%20lawyers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwindsurf-head-product-engineering-what-makes-successful-sofware-developer-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Windsurf%2C%20a%20coding%20assistance%20platform%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-collar-job-demand-growth-white-collar-layoffs-ai-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0physical%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-collar-job-demand-growth-white-collar-layoffs-ai-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20often%20among%20the%20lowest-paying%20jobs%2C%20is%20harder%20to%20tackle%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20back-breaking%20work%20that%20people%20do%20and%20still%20do%20it%2C%20and%20that's%20probably%20the%20hardest%20place%20to%20attack%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20thinking%20sort%20of%20much%20further%20out%2C%20which%20is%20like%20robots%2C%20it's%20like%20humanoids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Menlo%20Park-based%20firm%20specializes%20in%20investing%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-promising-startups-2024-according-top-vcs-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearly-stage%20tech%20and%20life%20science%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Founded%20in%201972%2C%20it%20has%20backed%20over%20900%20companies%2C%20including%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20improves%2C%20companies%20outside%20the%20tech%20industry%20are%20promoting%20or%20even%20mandating%20its%20use%20for%20their%20employees.%20That's%20leading%20to%20a%20rush%20of%20contracts%20for%20big%20companies%2C%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20startups%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Norway's%20%241.8%20trillion%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20said%20that%20using%20AI%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Bvoluntary%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20use%20it%2C%20you%20will%20never%20be%20promoted.%20You%20won't%20get%20a%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicolai%20Tangen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20viral%20memo%20in%20April%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopify-