d%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20British%20voice%20capable%20of%20rich%20emotions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20engineers%20then%20told%20Eve%20that%20they%20were%20at%20the%20product%20launch%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bwhisper%20something%20soothing%20to%20calm%20me%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20a%20deep%20breath%2C%20love.%20You've%20got%20this.%20It's%20just%20you%20and%20me%20having%20a%20quiet%20chat%20like%20we%20are%20tucked%20away%20in%20a%20cosy%20corner%20of%20a%20Yorkshire%20pub.%20The%20world's%20just%20a%20murmur%20out%20there.%20Feel%20that%20calm%20wash%20over%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20Eve%20said%20softly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20engineers%20also%20got%20Eve%20to%20sing%20an%20%26quot%3Bopera%20on%20Diet%20Coke.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BO%20Diet%20Coke%2C%20thou%20elixir%20divine%2C%20with%20bubbles%20that%20dance%20in%20a%20sparkling%20line!%20Thy%20crisp%2C%20cool%20kiss%2C%20on%20lips%20so%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Eve%20crooned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow's%20that%20for%20a%20mad%20little%20aria%3F%20Want%20me%20to%20belt%20out%20another%20verse%20or%20switch%20up%20the%20tune%3F%26quot%3B%20Eve%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22825d6371-2154-44e4-9744-5254b09cf831%5C%22%3EHow%20was%20Grok%20trained%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Grok%20LLM%20is%20trained%20on%20public%20sources%20and%20data%20sets.%20These%20sources%20are%20curated%20and%20audited%20by%20a%20set%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-elon-musk-hiring-ramp-up-data-annotators-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tutors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20more%20commonly%20known%20as%20data%20annotators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20Musk%20demanded%20immediate%20changes%20to%20Grok's%20training%20so%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-vows-to-make-xai-chatbot-grok-politically-neutral-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20politically%20neutral%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20February%202025%2C%20xAI%20employees%20told%20BI%20the%20company%20planned%20a%20hiring%20spree%20for%20AI%20tutors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20their%20training%20appeared%20to%20filter%20out%20any%20workers%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-grok-training-bias-woke-idealogy-2025-02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft-leaning%20beliefs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20internal%20training%20document%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20tutors%20were%20told%20to%20look%20out%20for%20%26quot%3Bwoke%20ideology%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcancel%20culture.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20said%20that%20Grok%20should%20avoid%20commenting%20on%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20phobias%26quot%3B%20like%20racism%2C%20Islamophobia%2C%20and%20antisemitism%20unless%20prompted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETen%20days%20before%20launching%20Grok-1.5%2C%20xAI%20opened%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-open-source-ai-grok-openai-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrok-1's%20source%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20public.%20The%20company%20has%20since%20published%20the%20subsequent%20Grok%20models%20on%20GitHub%2C%20so%20observers%20can%20see%20new%20changes%20to%20Grok's%20commands.%20That%20includes%20a%20recent%20change%20in%20which%20Grok%20was%20told%20to%20%26quot%3Bnot%20shy%20away%20from%20making%20claims%20which%20are%20politically%20incorrect%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20well%20substantiated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Musk%20said%20that%20AI%20models%20are%20trained%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-retrain-grok-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoo%20much%20garbage%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Musk%20planned%20to%20use%20Grok-3.5%20to%20%26quot%3Brewrite%20the%20entire%20corpus%20of%20human%20knowledge%2C%20adding%20missing%20information%20and%20deleting%20errors.%26quot%3B%20Then%2C%20he%20would%20retrain%20the%20next%20iteration%20of%20Grok%20on%20that%20new%20base%20of%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294721840-2712-4b9d-8b4c-7458018f8af1%5C%22%3EWhat's%20unique%20about%20Grok's%20output%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrok%20is%20fully%20integrated%20with%20Musk's%20social%20media%20site%2C%20X%2C%20and%20appears%20regularly%20in%20threads%20spanning%20various%20topics%20when%20users%20ask%20it%20to%20weigh%20in%20with%20jokes%2C%20commentary%2C%20or%20fact-checking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20companies'%20AI%20chatbots%2C%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20Grok's%20output%20is%20visible%20because%20of%20the%20bot's%20replies%20on%20X.%20The%20same%20level%20of%20scrutiny%20isn't%20readily%20available%20for%20some%20bots%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-named-chatgpt-in-a-late-night-decision-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20unless%20users%20publicly%20post%20screenshots%20of%20the%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20not%20all%20of%20Grok's%20responses%20are%20visible%20to%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20users%20can%20still%20chat%20privately%20with%20the%20bot%2C%20and%20it's%20unclear%20how%20those%20private%20responses%20compare%20to%20the%20ones%20on%20its%20public%20interface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20unique%20to%20Grok%20is%20xAI's%20approach%20to%20transparency%20surrounding%20the%20bot's%20system%20operations.%20The%20company%20publishes%20some%20base%20code%20and%20training%20prompt%20updates%20to%20a%20GitHub%20page%2C%20allowing%20viewers%20to%20inspect%2C%20critique%2C%20and%20better%20understand%20the%20model's%20development%20and%20behavior%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20developers%20can%20use%20and%20adapt%20the%20existing%20model%2C%20they%20cannot%20retrain%20Grok%20from%20scratch%20or%20fully%20understand%20the%20training%20processes%20involved%2C%20as%20its%20code%20is%20not%20entirely%20%3Ca%20href%