%20apartment%20building.%20A%20majority%20of%20Singaporeans%20reside%20in%20flats%20like%20hers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686b87d73d5881a51c1cc36b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChia's%20caf%C3%A9%20is%20located%20in%20a%20government-built%20apartment%20building.%20Most%20Singaporeans%20reside%20in%20flats%20like%20hers.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20spent%20SG%247%2C000%20on%20the%20equipment%20needed%20for%20a%20caf%C3%A9%3A%20an%20espresso%20machine%2C%20a%20coffee%20grinder%2C%20a%20small%20refrigerator%2C%20and%20some%20wooden%20tables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20May%2C%20she%20launched%20The%20Noob%20Coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8ea6ea1-722c-487a-835d-65308fa697a5%5C%22%3E%245%20drinks%20and%20homemade%20banana%20cake%2C%20served%20by%20a%20chatty%20grandmother%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChia%20said%20that%20despite%20her%20years%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20the%20closest%20she%20had%20come%20to%20making%20drinks%20was%20preparing%20sauces.%20She%20bought%20a%20coffee%20machine%20and%20grinder%20with%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20use%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20wanted%20a%20break%20from%20cooking%2C%20so%20she%20decided%20to%20launch%20a%20drinks-only%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20named%20it%20The%20Noob%20Coffee%20because%20I'm%20a%20noob%20to%20drinks.%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20starting%20afresh%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20menu%20includes%20basic%20black-and-white%20coffees%2C%20starting%20from%20SG%244.%20Her%20most%20popular%20concoctions%20are%20her%20Earl%20Gray%20matcha%20and%20strawberry%20and%20yogurt%20matcha%2C%20which%20cost%20SG%246%20and%20SG%246.50%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chia's%20Dirty%20Earl%20drink%2C%20a%20combination%20of%20Earl%20Grey%20and%20matcha%2C%20and%20a%20slice%20of%20homemade%20banana%20cake.%5C%