y%2C%20Chia%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20cure%20her%20dementia%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20I%20can%20slow%20its%20progress%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Chia%2C%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20take%20it%20easier.%20She%20says%20she%20starts%20her%20day%20by%20baking%20banana%20cake%20and%20having%20coffee%2C%20and%20she%20mans%20the%20operation%20from%2010%20a.m.%20to%206%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20metal%20sign%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20Chia's%20flat%20welcomes%20guests.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686b66b53d5881a51c1cc2e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20small%20metal%20sign%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20Chia's%20flat%20welcomes%20guests.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Les%20Amis%2C%20she%20said%20she%20barely%20interacted%20with%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20more%20accomplished%20because%20this%20is%20what%20I%20started%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20even%20though%20I'm%20tired%2C%20I%20still%20feel%20very%20fulfilled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-michelin-chef-after-grandmother-dementia-diagnosis-started-cafe-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752112643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68678a75f748d8c055f5010b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-michelin-chef-after-grandmother-dementia-diagnosis-started-cafe-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chia%20Jin%20Fang%20used%20to%20work%2014%20hours%20daily%20in%20a%20Michelin-starred%20restaurant.%20Now%2C%20she%20runs%20a%20small%20home-based%20caf%C3%A9%20while%20tending%20to%20her%20grandmother.%22%2C%2