%241.5%20trillion%20in%20collective%20assets%20is%20demanding%20that%20Tesla%20publicly%20announce%20an%20%26quot%3BAnnual%20General%20Meeting%26quot%3B%20date%2C%20disclose%20access%20details%2C%20and%20give%20shareholders%20%26quot%3Bsufficient%20time%20and%20information%20to%20engage%20meaningfully%20in%20the%20governance%20process.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThis%20lack%20of%20transparency%20raises%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20company's%20respect%20for%20shareholder%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20fiduciaries%2C%20we%20believe%20strong%20corporate%20governance%20and%20responsive%20board%20oversight%20are%20foundational%20to%20long-term%20company%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20is%20signed%20by%2027%20shareholders%2C%20including%20multiple%20large%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpennsylvania-pension-fund-halts-new-tesla-investments-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epension%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20state%20treasurers%2C%20such%20as%20New%20York%20City%20Comptroller%20Brad%20S.%20Lander%2C%20Oregon%20State%20Treasurer%20Elizabeth%20Steiner%2C%20and%20State%20of%20Maryland%20Comptroller%20Brooke%20E.%20Lierman.%20International%20funds%20from%20Denmark%20and%20Sweden%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Friends%20Fiduciary%20Corporation%2C%20a%20Quaker-aligned%20investment%20firm%2C%20have%20also%20signed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20and%20Tesla's%20impending%20deadline%20were%20first%20reported%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Thomas%2C%20CEO%20of%20Shareholder%20Association%20for%20Research%20and%20Education%2C%20the%20main%20signatory%20of%20the%20letter%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20has%20yet%20to%20hear%20back%20from%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%2C%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Canada-based%20advocacy%20group%20that%20advises%20funds%20with%20%24150%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20corporations%20usually%20provide%20notice%20at%20least%20two%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20a%20meeting%2C%20but%20Tesla%20has%20yet%20to%20do%20so%20%26quot%3Bas%20the%20clock%20starts%20to%20tick.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20definitely%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20global%20drop%20in%20sales%2C%20the%20share%20prices%20tanking%2C%20and%20the%20CEO's%20attention%20span%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that's%20why%20we%20want%20to%20have%20the%20meeting%2C%20not%20just%20because%20we%20like%20going%20to%20meetings%2C%20but%20because%20we%20actually%20think%20there%20are%20things%20that%20need%20to%20be%20discussed%20with%20shareholders%20in%20a%20transparent%20and%20accountable%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20just%20say%20this%2C%20that%20shareholders%20shouldn't%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20courts%20to%20enforce%20basic%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20added%20of%20Tesla.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20invested%20in%20it%20for%20a%20good%20reason%2C%20and%20as%20its%20returns%20and%20its%20sales%20and%20its%20performance%20tips%2C%20now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20intervene.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexas'%20Business%20Organization%20Code%20states%20that%20a%20court%20in%20the%20county%20where%20the%20company's%20principal%20executive%20office%20is%20located%20%26quot%3Bmay%20order%20a%20meeting%20to%20be%20held%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20company%20fails%20to%20hold%20the%20meeting%20or%20obtain%20written%20consent%20within%20a%2013-month%20period.%20For%20Tesla%2C%20that%20would%20be%20Travis%20County%2C%20where%20its%20Gigafactory%20Texas%20is%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20now%20has%20four%20days%20left%20to%20schedule%20a%20meeting%2C%20or%20the%20shareholders%20can%20take%20matters%20to%20a%20judge%2C%20who%20could%20compel%20a%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-headquarters-hq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0moved%20its%20head