d%20to%20give%20up%20because%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20college%20fees.%20His%20family%20had%20their%20struggle%20and%20Pintu%20too%20had%20to%20chip%20in%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeginning%20of%20the%20post-graduate%3Cem%3E%20Paanwala%20%3C%2Fem%3Echapter%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20were%20past%20our%20stipulated%20time%20of%20a%2030-minute%20interview%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20that%20Pintu%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20were%20not%20only%20personal%20but%20also%20a%20reflection%20of%20deep-rooted%20unfair%20practices%20of%20exploiting%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F462476%2Fdelhi-10-rupee-meals-ngo-humari-udaan-women-empowerment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20daily%20wage%20labourers.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20after%20dropping%20out%20of%20college%2C%20I%20went%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Emazdoori%20(daily-wage%20labour).%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20worked%20with%20a%20contractor%20for%20three%20months%2C%20and%20he%20kept%20on%20telling%20me%20that%20he%20would%20pay%20me%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20that%20never%20happened.%20There%20were%20several%20other%20instances%20where%20I%20was%20met%20with%20humiliation%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20of%20my%20own.%20With%20just%20Rs%201500%20in%20my%20pocket%2C%20I%20started%20my%20%3Cem%3EPaanwala%20dukaan%20%3C%2Fem%3Earound%201999.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2_11zon-1751956846.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Putul%20Pohan%2C%20Pintu's%20partner%20is%20seen%20at%20a%20gathering%20in%20the%20slum%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2_11zon-1751956846.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2_11zon-1751956846-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2_11zon-1751956846-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2_11zon-1751956846-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2_11zon-1751956846-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPutul%20Pohan%2C%20Pintu%E2%80%99s%20partner%20(L)%2C%20shares%20that%20she%20wishes%20to%20continue%20her%20studies%20if%20their%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20conditions%20improve%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20did%20his%20conviction%20to%20complete%20his%20educational%20endeavours%20end%20here%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20no.%20Pintu%20used%20to%20and%20even%20today%2C%20starts%20his%20day%20as%20early%20as%20six%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20keeps%20his%20shop%20open%20till%2011%20at%20night.%20He%20highlights%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20earn%20a%20little%20more%20than%20what%20others%20used%20to%20get%20from%20their%20%3Cem%3Epaan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshops%20because%20he%20had%20his%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20a%20writer%20to%20keep%20going%2C%20hence%20the%20extra-long%20work%20hours.%20And%20while%20managing%20his%20shop%2C%20he%20used%20to%20read%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20used%20to%20mock%20me%2C%20called%20me%20out%20for%20acting%20like%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%20But%20I%20took%20that%20as%20a%20compliment.%20Although%20my%20early%20writings%20had%20been%20published%20in%20the%20local%20newspapers%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20write%20books%20and%20become%20an%20author%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pintu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20all%20this%20while%2C%20Pintu%