t-caption%5C%22%3EMuppala%20study%20found%20a%20key%20understanding%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20chocolate%20inherently%20depends%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20started%20mapping%20and%20contextualizing%20the%20market%20to%20understand%20what%20chocolate%20is.%20%E2%80%9CI%20quickly%20realized%20that%20anybody%20involved%20in%20the%20chocolate%20industry%20in%20India%20is%20buying%20chocolate%2C%20melting%20it%2C%20moulding%20it%2C%20adding%20nuts%2C%20flavour%2C%20and%20sea%20salt%2C%20and%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F217619%2Fdark-chocolate-health-benefits-reduced-heart-risk-improved-brain-function-buy-online-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%3Epackaging%20it%20as%20their%20own%20chocolate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20enough%20sustainable%20differentiation%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hyderabad-based%20entrepreneur%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Almond%20House%2C%20he%20understood%20that%20mithai%20is%20regional.%20Every%20region%20has%20different%20preferences.%20I%20started%20realizing%20that%20our%20younger%20people%E2%80%99s%20moods%20are%20shifting%20from%20traditional%20categories%20like%20mithai%20to%20contemporary%20modern%20and%2C%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20Western%20categories%20like%20patisserie%20chocolates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20every%20city%20has%20two%20or%20three%20chocolate%20brands%20like%20his%20mithai%20brands%2C%20but%20if%20they%20all%20source%20the%20same%20ingredients%20from%20the%20same%20multinational%20supplier%2C%20the%20end%20product%20will%20be%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELiving%20with%20Farmers%2C%20Learning%20from%20the%20Soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20the%20art%20of%20chocolate%20making%2C%20small-batch%20chocolate%20production%2C%20and%20the%20principles%20of%20craft%20ch