3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20about%20working%20with%20them%20is%20the%20respect%20they%20have%20for%20our%20offering.%20They%20pay%20us%20above-market%20rates%20for%20our%20fruit%2C%20but%20more%20than%20that%2C%20we%20see%20the%20value%20of%20what%20we%20grow.%20When%20our%20cacao%20goes%20through%20their%20Fermentery%20with%20all%20the%20scientific%20fermentation%20and%20drying%20processes%20that%20they%20carry%20out%20and%20it%20is%20turned%20into%20fine%20flavour%20cacao%20beans%2C%20it%20gives%20us%20tremendous%20pride.%20We%20know%20exactly%20where%20our%20fruit%20is%20going%2C%20and%20we%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20made%20into%20something%20truly%20special.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20farmers%20here%20produced%20cocoa%20in%20a%20conventional%20method%2C%20Muppala%20faced%20another%20challenge%20related%20to%20the%20genetics%20of%20cocoa%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20history%20of%20its%20arrival%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-500x739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-500x739.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-203x300.jpg%20203w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-768x1135.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-1039x1536.jpg%201039w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-1386x2048.jpg%201386w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-150x222.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465025%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20Manam%20Chocolate%20Karkhana%2C%20processing%2C%20retailing%2C%20and%20crafting%20of%20chocolate%20are%20combined%20under%20a%20single%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20addressed%20the%20genetic%20problem%20through%20technological%20solutions%20developed%20by%20our%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Muppala%2C%20who%20noted%20that%20India%20grows%20only%200.5%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20cocoa.%20Even%20if%20the%20production%20were%20to%20increase%20fourfold%2C%20the%20output%20would%20only%20represent%202%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20cocoa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20area%20of%20land%20creates%20barriers%20to%20being%20a%20major%20player.%20The%20crop%20demands%20specific%20environmental%20conditions%2C%20including%20sufficient%20water%20and%20shade.%20It%20grows%20only%20between%2020%C2%B0%20north%20and%2020%C2%B0%20south%20of%20the%20Equator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20may%20never%20be%20a%20major%20cocoa-growing%20country%2C%20but%20we%20can%20make%20India%20a%20%E2%80%98premium%E2%80%99%20cocoa-growing%20nation.%20After%20having%20engaged%20over%20150%20farmers%20cultivating%20cocoa%20across%20a%20collective%20area%20of%203%2C000%20acres%20and%20making%20it%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20cocoa-growing%20region%2C%20we%20constructed%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20fine-flavour%20cocoa%20fermentary%20at%20Tadikalapudi%20in%20West%20Godavari%20on%20a%20four-acre%20land%20in%202021%2C%20where%20we%20execute%20fermentation%20and%20drying%20with%20our%20advanced%20scientific%20technique%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muppala%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20story%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehalwai%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20wanted%20to%20craft%20chocolate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20270%20people%20worked%20on%20this%20project%20over%20four%20years%2C%20culminating%20in%20its%20launch.%20Muppala%20realized%20he%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehalwai%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20wanted%20to%20craft%20chocolate%20but%20ended%20up%20making%20something%20else.%20What%20about%20chocolate%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20came%20back%20to%20Hyderabad%20and%20started%20structuring%20what%20chocolate%20can%20be%20and%20should%20be%20for%20India%20as%20well%20as%20from%20India%20for%20the%20world.%20It%E2%80%99s%20our%20social%20proclivity%20as%20Indians%20to%20gift%2C%20share%2C%20and%20consume%20sweets%2C%E2%80%9D%20mentions%20Muppala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuppala%20has%20invested%20significantly%20in%20the%20business%2C%20including%20creating%20the%20Manam%20Chocolate%20Karkhana%2C%20where%20the%20processing%2C%20retailing%2C%20and%20crafting%20of%20chocolate%20are%20combined%20under%20a%20single%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpanning%20an%20area%20of%2010%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20the%20Karkhana%20offers%20a%20chance%20to%20discover%2C%20explore%2C%20experience%2C%20and%20engage%20with%20cacao%20and%20chocolate%20in%20a%20dynamic%20and%20interactive%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%