coa%20through%20a%20blockchain-enabled%20system.%20Every%20single%20bean%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20its%20exact%20farm.%20However%2C%20the%20supermarket%20chocolate%20provides%20no%20information%20about%20the%20source%20of%20the%20cocoa%20bean%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muppala%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkhana%20is%20now%20reaping%20the%20rewards.%20In%20its%20first%20year%2C%20the%20company%2C%20which%20employs%20around%20200%20people%2C%20recorded%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs.%208.79%20crore%2C%20achieved%20in%20only%20eight%20months%20of%20operation%20during%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023-24.%20The%20chocolate%20maker%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20growing%20150%25%20year-on-year.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20successful%20market%20strategy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20imports%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20its%20cocoa%20needs%20despite%20having%20grown%20cocoa%20for%20over%20six%20decades.%20Muppala%20recently%20started%20exporting%20beans%20to%20the%20world.%20This%20February%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20major%20consignment%20of%20fine%20flavoured%20cocoa%20has%20been%20exported%20from%20India%20to%20Switzerland%2C%20where%20a%20major%20Swiss%20chocolate%20brand%20is%20making%20a%20single-origin%20India%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20farmers%2C%20fermenters%2C%20chocolate%20makers%2C%20chocolatiers%2C%20and%20storytellers.%20We%20see%20ourselves%20as%20craftspeople.%20Starting%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20who%20craft%20at%20the%20source%2C%20then%20a%20fermenter%2C%20then%20a%20chocolate%20maker.%20Our%20story%20starts%20on%20the%20farms.%20Every%20store%20we%20open%2C%20our%20farmer%20has%20to%20open%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20concludes%20the%20chocolate%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20it%20take%20to%20create%20fine-flavour%20cocoa%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20agro-climatic%20conditions%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoyapati%20Venkateswara%20Rao%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20mem